                    </button>
                    <p class="mt-2"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
                      Methods that help students in scheduling study sessions efficiently include:<br>
                      <ol>
                        <li>schedule(): Allows student to schedule new study sessions</li>
                        <li>cancel(): Enables cancelling existing study sessions</li>
                        <li>update(): Allows modification of the date and duration of the study session</li>
                      </ol>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
