            <!-- LEARNING OUTCOMES -->
            <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center mt-5">
              <div class="col-12">
                <div class="project-card-large bg-white">
                  <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5 class="card-title" style="color:#0d6efd;">Learning Outcomes</h5>
                    <p>
                      Designed and implemented a modular OOP system in Python.<br><br>
                      Applied encapsulation and collaboration across multiple classes (Student, Subjects, Task, StudySession, Reminder, Planner).<br><br>
                      Built a functional console application simulating real-world academic planning.<br><br>
                      Implemented task prioritization based on subject priority, completion status, and deadlines.<br><br>
                      Included automatic study session suggestions linked to tasks.<br><br>
                      Demonstrated meaningful object collaboration and method usage in a student-focused planning system.
                    </p>
                  </div>
